{"type": "article", "id": 17839, "title": "羊毛制作的宠物小窝", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-20T07:10:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607183500BlZ2mDbNJzacMV6U.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是乌克兰的设计师 Anna Mo 自制的宠物小窝，她购买了产自澳洲的美丽诺羊毛和两根超大的木针，手工编成粗线条的交叉纹路，在柔软舒适之余带去温暖的感受。此外，她还编织了衣服，使粗线条的羊毛像一片片树叶，有 15 种颜色可选，目前在 etsy 上出售，<a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/listing/245166707/super-lush-pet-bed-cozy-basket-for-dog?ref=shop_home_active_24\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183458Q3jVoyOlXeugpfFm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183458Hqj4eUEZ96FQWMwD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183459WYdih8wu1RK0mHDS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183459WbyQhVrkxvj9we2Y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183500RuU9DCyjL0aZnJbc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}